codex
The soft-skin path uses `VertexBufferVector`, so the relevant binding is the multi-stream IA path, not only `ms_currentVBOffset`. I’ve found that vector bind computes byte offsets as `getOffset() * getVertexSize()` and passes the same `getVertexSize()` as IA stride.
